**1 — memoize, zero shape change.**
Wrap the object you already pass to <Outlet context={{...}}> in useMemo. No field is added, removed, or renamed; every consumer of useOutletContext<IabdOutletContext>() gets the identical shape. This is a 5-line diff, purely a correctness/perf fix, and the easiest possible PR to review and trust.

const outletContextValue = useMemo(() => ({
  employmentTaxData, setEmploymentTaxData, dynamicIABDVals, /* ...all current fields... */
}), [employmentTaxData, dynamicIABDVals, /* ...matching deps... */]);

<Outlet context={outletContextValue} />


